{"tid":1152132,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"輸了加犯法。。迷芒中","createTime":"2019-05-12T18:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T08:15:14.000Z","uid":181819,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6af98c538aa5ed26f784dc071259422dbd93aaf8","tid":1152132,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:19:15.000Z","msg":"今天補領回身份證 ，就出發，也是出事日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今天海記失控收場，海記門口賣船飛阿姐，問我:細佬，想唔想追數，叫我交身份証即比5萬我追，如果追到有人會抽我水，追唔到最多慢慢還<br />\n<br />\n當時乜都冇諗只想追回4千<br />\n諗住5皮本好易追4千<br />\n<br />\n點知黑起上來，500平注<br />\n西5口先win 1口<br />\n<br />\n5皮朱到去2皮失控<br />\n5k5k一口<br />\n連西4口，8朱9<br />\n<br />\n之後當然有人送我返香港<br />\n係船上，我問佢息口幾多<br />\n佢話9出13歸，自己計，之後去到香港 海域<br />\n搶左我電話，打比我老母叫佢準備錢<br />\n如何如何，又話一陣落船去旺角金鸡廣場見佢老闆，我好驚<br />\n落船过關，佢比返身份証我<br />\n<br />\n我狗闖去叫救命，條友閃左人<br />\n但電話係佢度，海關問我咩事<br />\n我直接講出所有野，佢叫我自己報警<br />\n大約用左20分鐘，出到佢，原來佢係門口等我<br />\n仲有兩個mk仔共3人<br />\n<br />\n我落電梯果時，佢地係咁拍我頭<br />\n又鬧我，我忍冇可忍同佢地爭執起來<br />\n我話拍一下一萬，之後打起黎<br />\n其中一個mk 碌咗落樓梯<br />\n之後上咗差館<br />\n<br />\n另外兩個 做證人話我出以傷害他人身體<br />\n頭先有個財仔 打電話畀我<br />\n有事慢慢傾<br />\n<br />\n我哋求財 叫我明天早時去佢哋 寫字樓"},{"pid":"da93b0ed717794691985f7548577ed3c8e27f40d","tid":1152132,"uid":73340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輸左就還錢啦<br />\n死賭仔"},{"pid":"dbc2b379a83e0d84410a45e6132bb71ad8b56185","tid":1152132,"uid":136508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:28:06.000Z","msg":"打起上黎真係蝕..<br />\n<br />\n建議問銀行借筆錢 還左比班財仔先 傷人果單佢地收左錢應該無數放過你"},{"pid":"a708d6d7125acf8a59758b1f2a9b7976c72b8e05","tid":1152132,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:29:26.000Z","msg":"5皮野唔洗走佬喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80aae62a708b9a9b0fee744a95009aa7b0d122af","tid":1152132,"uid":242630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:31:35.000Z","msg":"根本就無得翻身，你睇你幾賤格，完全係你自做成，搞到咁，返唔到轉頭，聽日好難面對，你係可以選擇唔面對，跳啦"},{"pid":"6138318c0bb6a9d45ab7c324fbd68a86d48b3c69","tid":1152132,"uid":229955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:51:11.000Z","msg":"殘體字"},{"pid":"17cc5b8a655a4b6d2ff7f1ebf51b7af1c2da9241","tid":1152132,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:59:57.000Z","msg":"香討<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4619722573c9b8cf03b02ef20d8fd3c8b5800bb","tid":1152132,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:06:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞你嘅入台證啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入台證問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/892554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/892554</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b93560a73e04594e55850f8cb869c0ef84d1c2c","tid":1152132,"uid":171611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:36:41.000Z","msg":"借錢咪還錢，又無人迫你借"},{"pid":"2cc3b8a5b1f5fe86bdabd28a67e3e0d1a11884d2","tid":1152132,"uid":20291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"屌又係香土膠post"},{"pid":"067b265f0fe1990da13f5301043cfedb3167bfc0","tid":1152132,"uid":99720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"拍一下一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8baadcbe67d03eabca9d590e8aff3554ee61